   "source": [
    "# %% [markdown]\n",
    "# # 📊 Daily Orders Data Generation\n",
    "# \n",
    "# This notebook generates **6 months of synthetic daily order data** for every\n",
    "# restaurant in the master dataset.\n",
    "# \n",
    "# ### Simulated Patterns\n",
    "# | Pattern | Effect |\n",
    "# |---|---|\n",
    "# | **Weekend surge** | 30–50% higher orders on Sat & Sun |\n",
    "# | **Holiday peaks** | 50–100% higher orders on public holidays |\n",
    "# | **Weekday patterns** | Mon–Fri baseline with day-specific multipliers |\n",
    "# | **Restaurant-specific base demand** | Derived from votes, rating & price range |\n",
    "# | **Seasonal trends** | Gradual monthly variation (sine curve) |\n",
    "# | **Random noise** | Gaussian noise for realistic variance |\n",
    "# | **Promotions & discounts** | Random promotion events with discount impact |\n",
    "# \n",
    "# **Output →** `data/raw/daily_orders.csv`"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "ea7912fc",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2026-03-01T18:15:19.925941Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2026-03-01T18:15:19.925328Z",
     "iopub.status.idle": "2026-03-01T18:15:21.298049Z",
     "shell.execute_reply": "2026-03-01T18:15:21.297645Z"
    }
   },
